fields.bio: Mr. Pratap Bag is a highly qualified and experienced healthcare practitioner specializing in physiotherapy and alternative medicine. With extensive training in multiple healing modalities, he provides comprehensive healthcare services focusing on natural healing and holistic wellness.
fields.education: Master of Doctor in Acupuncture, Master of Bachelor Science, Diploma in Massage Therapy, Diploma in Physiotherapy, and various other certifications in alternative medicine.
fields.previous_experience: Former trainer at S.B. Yoga Medical College, Ex-IBMer, Author of "Acupressure Tips"
fields.philosophy: Believes in holistic healing approach combining traditional and modern therapeutic techniques for optimal patient care.

fields.testimonial: Mr. Pratap Bag's treatment was excellent. His acupressure therapy completely relieved my chronic back pain. Highly recommended for anyone looking for natural healing.
The holistic approach and personalized care I received was amazing. The massage therapy sessions helped me manage stress better than any medication.
As an athlete, I needed specialized care for my injury. The physiotherapy sessions were professional and effective. I recovered faster than expected.
